column10:
My first time journaling, and I like the app so far, but it’s quite glitchy. Whenever I’m editing a previous paragraph, the cursor moves on its own to the bottom of my entry. Happens all the time. Very annoying. 

Please add the following:

- A way to undelete journal entries;
- Folders, so we can journal for different things (eg work, personal, etc)/Ability to group entries by weeks/months;
- A feature that helps/reminds you to follow-up on an entry;
- Ability to format text within the app (eg add bullet points/checklists, etc);
- Enable hyperlinks;
- Ability to share entries (email/social media);

Basically, please make it an improved version of notes. 🙂
